{"tid":26082,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"CU CS>City CS?","createTime":"2016-12-06T13:36:51.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-29T09:26:48.000Z","uid":8380,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7cb160e6b02ecf772737a038851b31b25f9a730f","tid":26082,"uid":8380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T13:36:51.000Z","msg":"細佬對computer science 有興趣暫時bandA有放cu engineering同city cs<br />\n各位巴絲點睇呢兩科 其他u CS又如何"},{"pid":"5204ac3da4495be95e5113840de04a3a009fbc90","tid":26082,"uid":38316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T05:49:52.000Z","msg":"CS 最好<br />\n<br />\nUST 比較辛苦<br />\nHKU 你要預語文要好啲<br />\nCity 近幾年無以前咁好"},{"pid":"9c13dee4c9b233dc6935920f20b08fdbac5d4789","tid":26082,"uid":38316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T05:50:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>CU 最好<br />\n<br />\nUST 比較辛苦<br />\nHKU 你要預語文要好啲<br />\nCity 近幾年無以前咁好</blockquote>"},{"pid":"4d287a0655e91fefee20febcc96d204de21d6352","tid":26082,"uid":56101,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T06:01:07.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"a8f08243617f699a2b96fc075cfe7d1e89106ef9","tid":26082,"uid":45408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T06:14:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>CS 最好<br />\n<br />\nUST 比較辛苦<br />\nHKU 你要預語文要好啲<br />\nCity 近幾年無以前咁好</blockquote><br />\nCU都好撚辛苦 應該話cs一定好chur"},{"pid":"5249657897526c89614704ea34d2cfa010c97d7d","tid":26082,"uid":22116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T06:43:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>CS 最好<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nUST 比較辛苦<br />\n<br />\nHKU 你要預語文要好啲<br />\n<br />\nCity 近幾年無以前咁好</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nCU都好撚辛苦 <span style=\"color: red;\">應該話cs一定好chur</span></blockquote><br />\n正解<br />\nCU同UST CS差唔多辛苦<br />\nHKU詳情唔知，不過唔夠CU/UST 深入technical，可能著重Business方面D掛<br />\nCity只可以話係好過poly"},{"pid":"230338749284d9f06ae2b59316bdeb97151bdd92","tid":26082,"uid":38316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T09:51:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>CS 最好<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nUST 比較辛苦<br />\n<br />\nHKU 你要預語文要好啲<br />\n<br />\nCity 近幾年無以前咁好</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nCU都好撚辛苦 <span style=\"color: red;\">應該話cs一定好chur</span></blockquote><br />\n正解<br />\nCU同UST CS差唔多辛苦<br />\nHKU詳情唔知，不過唔夠CU/UST 深入technical，可能著重Business方面D掛<br />\nCity只可以話係好過poly</blockquote><br />\n首先我唔係好明點樣為之深入？<br />\nundergrad 既課程其實都係入門啫<br />\n&ldquo;基本嘢&rdquo;嚟講近乎間間都齊<br />\n唯一例外好似得CU 既automata 係必修？<br />\n<br />\nundergrad 我始終唔同意鬥讀書多鬥讀得深，學識點樣用啲基本嘢先係最重要<br />\n<br />\n同埋UST 辛苦係佢拉curve 玩得比較chur"},{"pid":"f857d0d4b93033b15b38a0320994abbf8a6f118c","tid":26082,"uid":16903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T10:06:25.000Z","msg":"其實一直都係講個名 所以三大&gt;poly city <br />\n教既野唔會差太遠 都係oop, discrete math, algorithm 果啲 然後先揀stream <br />\nCU cs要搶major UST 辛苦冇ulife <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"351dd675ca427c064836725575b261439881550c","tid":26082,"uid":35034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T10:14:18.000Z","msg":"有無city cs 巴絲講下幾分入到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73d4902347a70562918c064f66230349afc13ff4","tid":26082,"uid":33057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T10:32:58.000Z","msg":"city cs要做placement 可chur可唔chur<br />\nUST cs聽講可以揀做唔做fyp"},{"pid":"4941181a9d03b9dbffdc8b36b8da7eabef049245","tid":26082,"uid":1123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T11:06:15.000Z","msg":"Cu cs 好多course 得個名唔開<br />\n又走左個好正嘅prof<br />\n今年仲要有條stream 冇開course 搞到有班人可能畢唔到業<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋中大要成車foundation course 係阻鳩你成個year 1 eg math 讀返哂 d in matrix vector(唔係全部冇用嘅 有d course 有關 但你唔讀個elective 就冇用)<br />\n仲要讀physics <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之後year1 仲要夠gpa ~3.0 先入到<br />\n入到去又係另一個狂chur<br />\n今年cs 人聖誕都有deadline<br />\n但之前仲有幾科final 嫁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你諗下一次過讀幾科cs<br />\n一科關os 一科關 algo 一科關 formal languages 有d 人仲讀多科 database<br />\n每科d assignment 層層疊咁<br />\n仲有d general edu course 中文英文<br />\n<br />\n如果你本身冇底 唔係好建議你入<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nCUCS grad 留名"},{"pid":"0f2d9c710447601c95f283c2cedd498f88b7c45f","tid":26082,"uid":11040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T13:22:27.000Z","msg":"岩岩3150 final仆街完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79025f3cc200b0f4778a90c4d02410cc0c984c2c","tid":26082,"uid":56101,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T14:32:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>岩岩3150 final仆街完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n成頁半嘅code揾一行bug<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 真係see u next sem <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13282c0b6441f44d8c45288ff88933d967fa9ef7","tid":26082,"uid":1123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T16:09:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>岩岩3150 final仆街完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n成頁半嘅code揾一行bug<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 真係see u next sem <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n冇左mole 神嘅cucs 真係含撚"},{"pid":"a67814222395823aa2b1c216178a4a3dd0bb654f","tid":26082,"uid":8380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T05:09:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Cu cs 好多course 得個名唔開<br />\n又走左個好正嘅prof<br />\n今年仲要有條stream 冇開course 搞到有班人可能畢唔到業<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋中大要成車foundation course 係阻鳩你成個year 1 eg math 讀返哂 d in matrix vector(唔係全部冇用嘅 有d course 有關 但你唔讀個elective 就冇用)<br />\n仲要讀physics <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之後year1 仲要夠gpa ~3.0 先入到<br />\n入到去又係另一個狂chur<br />\n今年cs 人聖誕都有deadline<br />\n但之前仲有幾科final 嫁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你諗下一次過讀幾科cs<br />\n一科關os 一科關 algo 一科關 formal languages 有d 人仲讀多科 database<br />\n每科d assignment 層層疊咁<br />\n仲有d general edu course 中文英文<br />\n<br />\n如果你本身冇底 唔係好建議你入<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nCUCS grad 留名</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n讀緊phy ict 但phy真唔掂 唔怕chur<br />\ngrad咗宜家做緊咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae5f45498daced6defa0c05ea40467919407a720","tid":26082,"uid":8380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T05:10:54.000Z","msg":"順便問 ee同cs最大分別係咩"},{"pid":"1fa8c343163f792eec38b4e7e8a22088d5ace7c8","tid":26082,"uid":31752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T05:14:27.000Z","msg":"UG讀乜撚都係垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n讀左三年書最大得著就係<br />\n所有野都可以係google竹月"},{"pid":"71cacc78c14488d7a25103b1e3b8533e9b2128f0","tid":26082,"uid":31752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T05:14:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>UG讀乜撚都係垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n讀左三年書最大得著就係<br />\n所有野都可以係google學</blockquote>"},{"pid":"3edc9ebff7591b0bee24241aeb5d517b588664f5","tid":26082,"uid":33057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T05:15:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>順便問 ee同cs最大分別係咩</blockquote><br />\n數底差一定唔可以讀ee<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23520ee63901eabb32fe47cfbcfe86c0eba800d7","tid":26082,"uid":8380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T05:26:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>順便問 ee同cs最大分別係咩</blockquote><br />\n數底差一定唔可以讀ee<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n數底都ok 但phy差 ee洗唔洗掂phy"},{"pid":"9787c378a0a1569241681c6b3479bcbe2d0966f6","tid":26082,"uid":22116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T05:28:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>CS 最好<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nUST 比較辛苦<br />\n<br />\nHKU 你要預語文要好啲<br />\n<br />\nCity 近幾年無以前咁好</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nCU都好撚辛苦 <span style=\"color: red;\">應該話cs一定好chur</span></blockquote><br />\n正解<br />\nCU同UST CS差唔多辛苦<br />\nHKU詳情唔知，不過唔夠CU/UST 深入technical，可能著重Business方面D掛<br />\nCity只可以話係好過poly</blockquote><br />\n首先我唔係好明點樣為之深入？<br />\nundergrad 既課程其實都係入門啫<br />\n&ldquo;基本嘢&rdquo;嚟講近乎間間都齊<br />\n唯一例外好似得CU 既automata 係必修？<br />\n<br />\nundergrad 我始終唔同意鬥讀書多鬥讀得深，學識點樣用啲基本嘢先係最重要<br />\n<br />\n同埋UST 辛苦係佢拉curve 玩得比較chur</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n入門還入門，入門之中都有程度之分<br />\n特別係去到os依類底層既course就更加明顯睇到教得幾deep<br />\n<br />\n讀得深唔深唔係由學生決定，prof咁教咁出卷你就要讀，除非你唔介意爛grade去自學其他野又另一個玩法<br />\n<br />\n重有唔好同我講ust拉curve，有邊間u唔係拉curve，你咁講同考評局話dse唔係拉curve有咩分別，你係重視個成績既就拉唔拉curve都讀得辛苦架啦"},{"pid":"37216ba695e276b9cf9b01724bef90034691fcb0","tid":26082,"uid":1169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T05:45:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>順便問 ee同cs最大分別係咩</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n數底差一定唔可以讀ee<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n數底都ok 但phy差 ee洗唔洗掂phy</blockquote><br />\n大量<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8369e78d1c73406e77e6ac924bc9ff61cf330ed0","tid":26082,"uid":8380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T05:47:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>順便問 ee同cs最大分別係咩</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n數底差一定唔可以讀ee<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n數底都ok 但phy差 ee洗唔洗掂phy</blockquote><br />\n大量<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁睇我唔適合讀ee"},{"pid":"7d8fcc535028c126de7f806071931e3ac0bb1952","tid":26082,"uid":57006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T05:49:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>CS 最好<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nUST 比較辛苦<br />\n<br />\nHKU 你要預語文要好啲<br />\n<br />\nCity 近幾年無以前咁好</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nCityU CS programming 功課簡單過EE 好多倍<br />\n又有最少9個月 placement，迫要人做廉價勞工，同時又要人夜間返學。<br />\n<br />\n大部分tutorial 支那mphil phd教，佢地好似唔識講英文，ee哦哦咁都唔知up 乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00181449cd557afd0be164cbddfed0f7455e86b2","tid":26082,"uid":25334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T05:50:44.000Z","msg":"city ee chur撚過city cs<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申：city ee仔"},{"pid":"76df1e1ddd14c5847e239056a3807481a28fe1d3","tid":26082,"uid":49153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T05:51:54.000Z","msg":"搭單問<br />\ncomputer science 同computer engineering有咩分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nphy同ict都有5 讀乜好科<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae4cf2684b232f8e569e4b2a10a3cae3ce061b48","tid":26082,"uid":1123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T05:52:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>Cu cs 好多course 得個名唔開<br />\n又走左個好正嘅prof<br />\n今年仲要有條stream 冇開course 搞到有班人可能畢唔到業<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋中大要成車foundation course 係阻鳩你成個year 1 eg math 讀返哂 d in matrix vector(唔係全部冇用嘅 有d course 有關 但你唔讀個elective 就冇用)<br />\n仲要讀physics <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之後year1 仲要夠gpa ~3.0 先入到<br />\n入到去又係另一個狂chur<br />\n今年cs 人聖誕都有deadline<br />\n但之前仲有幾科final 嫁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你諗下一次過讀幾科cs<br />\n一科關os 一科關 algo 一科關 formal languages 有d 人仲讀多科 database<br />\n每科d assignment 層層疊咁<br />\n仲有d general edu course 中文英文<br />\n<br />\n如果你本身冇底 唔係好建議你入<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nCUCS grad 留名</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n讀緊phy ict 但phy真唔掂 唔怕chur<br />\ngrad咗宜家做緊咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nIT狗喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nPhy 有科仔讀 力學同 d in 數"},{"pid":"ed4b917b611c94506be3790f314f7d210532c01f","tid":26082,"uid":25334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T05:52:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>CS 最好<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nUST 比較辛苦<br />\n<br />\nHKU 你要預語文要好啲<br />\n<br />\nCity 近幾年無以前咁好</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nCityU CS programming 功課簡單過EE 好多倍<br />\n又有最少9個月 placement，迫要人做廉價勞工，同時又要人夜間返學。<br />\n<br />\n大部分tutorial 支那mphil phd教，佢地好似唔識講英文，ee哦哦咁都唔知up 乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nee冇placement都要由朝返到晚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，各有各慘啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6824bd17c72432ea90c969bb91393aacea8710db","tid":26082,"uid":6658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T06:01:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>CS 最好<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nUST 比較辛苦<br />\n<br />\nHKU 你要預語文要好啲<br />\n<br />\nCity 近幾年無以前咁好</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nCityU CS programming 功課簡單過EE 好多倍<br />\n又有最少9個月 placement，迫要人做廉價勞工，同時又要人夜間返學。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">大部分tutorial 支那mphil phd教，佢地好似唔識講英文，ee哦哦咁都唔知up 乜</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其他major都係咁啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62dd05c365fc5c87cdfd82e620ac470aea8c95c3","tid":26082,"uid":8380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T06:04:05.000Z","msg":"點睇 information system呢科"},{"pid":"2e11d1f13ebe45bbeccf5047d21d33b0baa6296d","tid":26082,"uid":33057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T06:04:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>搭單問<br />\n<br />\ncomputer science 同computer engineering有咩分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nphy同ict都有5 讀乜好科<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nce咪cs溝埋ee咁囉<br />\n但係ce係ee dept<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n都係果句 數底差唔好讀ee<br />\n係M2果d數唔係maths果d"},{"pid":"2831af111da1af419a85def0ae22d337ddb6f460","tid":26082,"uid":33057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T06:05:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><br />\nCityU CS programming 功課簡單過EE 好多倍<br />\n又有最少9個月 placement，迫要人做廉價勞工，同時又要人夜間返學。<br />\n大部分tutorial 支那mphil phd教，佢地好似唔識講英文，ee哦哦咁都唔知up 乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nee冇placement都要由朝返到晚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，各有各慘啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n番過placement有實際工作經驗其實冇咩唔好"},{"pid":"3d3f12fb415fdb8b7d19179117a95ac88ba71a1a","tid":26082,"uid":31178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"ci