學學嘅Pascal好似<br />\n<br />\n到底做唔做IT狗好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nIt工好多種類，program, network, security, consulting, big data, server。又有唔同role ba consultant pm engineer support又有分inhouse si vendor。睇下自己興趣囉。"},{"pid":"3621b86483a0e6a03a1aed4d0a618beecad5ae21","tid":26082,"uid":45055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T06:48:16.000Z","msg":"in cu cs we trust <br />\n<br />\n利申：a1 cu engine <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"373fbb219ea79962d86c5663124f40e92fdbdaac","tid":26082,"uid":8380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T06:49:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>in cu cs we trust <br />\n<br />\n利申：a1 cu engine <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都放咗 cu engine喺a1"},{"pid":"8815d19b420c2a5a075aaa09f1bbabcbbc4ecc4b","tid":26082,"uid":33057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T06:50:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>搭單問<br />\ncomputer science 同computer engineering有咩分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nphy同ict都有5 讀乜好科<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nce咪cs溝埋ee咁囉<br />\n但係ce係ee dept<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n都係果句 數底差唔好讀ee<br />\n係M2果d數唔係maths果d</blockquote><br />\n自問數底唔差唔勁<br />\n但係冇讀過m2<br />\n大電又唔夠分讀 嗚呀<br />\n咁mechanical engineering呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其他答你唔到<br />\n只可以話CS係咁多engine入面係計最少數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38a580ddd586ea2fb65eef3322e9563a3d97796c","tid":26082,"uid":19728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T06:54:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\nCityU CS programming 功課簡單過EE 