blockquote><br />\nce咪cs溝埋ee咁囉<br />\n但係ce係ee dept<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n都係果句 數底差唔好讀ee<br />\n係M2果d數唔係maths果d</blockquote><br />\n自問數底唔差唔勁<br />\n但係冇讀過m2<br />\n大電又唔夠分讀 嗚呀<br />\n咁mechanical engineering呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其他答你唔到<br />\n只可以話CS係咁多engine入面係計最少數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n數差就唔好讀engine<br />\n9成course 都係要計數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"468a767b88b2541fbe8fc29e69b4750d288d3304","tid":26082,"uid":33057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T06:58:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>點睇 information system呢科</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n見你讀ict有冇話鍾意D咩先<br />\n<br />\n基本上ict既野全部都係CS野黎</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\ndatabase嗰啲</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁一定CS啦唔洗諗</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 點解 咁IS都有啲database嘅</blockquote><br />\n有D即係點先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nCS可以讀到data science, big data果d<br />\n仲有programming, networking...上面有人數左"},{"pid":"7eddad45659eabf9a6795692e1991efa55ce565b","tid":26082,"uid":33057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T07:24:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\nCityU CS programming 功課簡單過EE 好多倍<br />\n<br />\n又有最少9個月 placement，迫要人做廉價勞工，同時又要人夜間返學。<br />\n<br />\n大部分tutorial 支那mphil phd教，佢地好似唔識講英文，ee哦哦咁都唔知up 乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nee冇placement都要由朝返到晚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />