gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n問題係唔chur 又學唔到野<br />\n<br />\n你都知cityu cs 啲course 幾少野架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nEe core 讀75credits<br />\n<br />\nCs core 又係75 credits<br />\n<br />\n但係cs 有12 credits 係placement <br />\n<br />\n同埋另外有9 credits 都係廢<br />\n<br />\n計返讀少好多野<br />\n<br />\n就要靠placement chur 嚟補返<br />\n<br />\n但係又好辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nCItyU CS core 少野係真 (唔計自己選擇electives)<br />\n除左software design / design and analyze of algorithm，其他野以前讀IVE computer engineering都教過</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n讀elective 仲仆街<br />\nElective 係學到好多野<br />\n但係佢係同placement year 重疊<br />\n即係搞到仲撚chur"},{"pid":"e3d4e79be41387cc30bbb3da56f7f23e34027c2c","tid":26082,"uid":49153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T10:31:52.000Z","msg":"都係諗唔透做engine佬定it狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n基本上改變一生嘅決定 好難落手 識嘅野又唔夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bef03bfb5d1919d1039d97ccdf00aeb064f02c71","tid":26082,"uid":33057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T10:39:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>都係諗唔透做engine佬定it狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n基本上改變一生嘅決定 好難落手 識嘅野又唔夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n做IT狗要偷人奶飲俾人拉<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c92225d1af368963730524667befc6959d8b1bd","tid":26082,"uid":45055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T10:53:28.000Z","msg":"入cu會唔會gpa太低揀唔到cs<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？"},{"pid":"a27d31395caf152a082105ba0537bb202453ea8e","tid":26082,"uid":57006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T10:58:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n<br />\n讀elective 仲仆街<br />\n<br />\nElective 係學到好多野<br />\n<br />\n但係佢係同placement year 重疊<br />\n<br />\n即係搞到仲撚chur</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nCityU CS<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有得揀 都唔會揀"},{"pid":"5cc23b48cf6d40f0136e67883a397f069a691f93","tid":26082,"uid":35965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T10:59:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>搭單問<br />\ncomputer science 同computer engineering有咩分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nphy同ict都有5 讀乜好科<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\ncs學software為主。ce學得low level d，eg assembly vhdl。你google下就知d code差幾遠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nassembly睇到頭都大<br />\nvhdl就同我中學學嘅Pascal好似<br />\n<br />\n到底做唔做IT狗好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nvhdl係用來做 IC 完全唔係&quot;Programming language''"},{"pid":"cc642727ac2171a8ab29005e9c5a499615401628","tid":26082,"uid":35965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T11:01:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>都係諗唔透做engine佬定it狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n基本上改變一生嘅決定 好難落手 識嘅野又唔夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n做 IT狗人工高過 細電狗好多"},{"pid":"6602c9b54f86988f9ddaad2909be5316eba4d6d6","tid":26082,"uid":59136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T11:05:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Cu cs 好多course 得個名唔開<br />\n又走左個好正嘅prof<br />\n今年仲要有條stream 冇開course 搞到有班人可能畢唔到業<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋中大要成車foundation course 係阻鳩你成個year 1 eg math 讀返哂 d in matrix vector(唔係全部冇用嘅 有d course 有關 但你唔讀個elective 就冇用)<br />\n仲要讀physics <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之後year1 仲要夠gpa ~3.0 先入到<br />\n入到去又係另一個狂chur<br />\n今年cs 人聖誕都有deadline<br />\n但之前仲有幾科final 嫁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你諗下一次過讀幾科cs<br />\n一科關os 一科關 algo 一科關 formal languages 有d 人仲讀多科 database<br />\n每科d assignment 層層疊咁<br />\n仲有d general edu course 中文英文<br />\n<br />\n如果你本身冇底 唔係好建議你入<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nCUCS grad 留名</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n冇左呀mole<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n同意有底先好入<br />\n本身過chur<br />\n冇底既話chur得黎好絕望"},{"pid":"bfb8d126c5483dbb81406377686dbf9746b07382","tid":26082,"uid":59136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T11:09:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>搭單問<br />\ncomputer science 同computer engineering有咩分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nphy同ict都有5 讀乜好科<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nce咪cs溝埋ee咁囉<br />\n但係ce係ee dept<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n都係果句 數底差唔好讀ee<br />\n係M2果d數唔係maths果d</blockquote><br />\n自問數底唔差唔勁<br />\n但係冇讀過m2<br />\n大電又唔夠分讀 嗚呀<br />\n咁mechanical engineering呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其他答你唔到<br />\n只可以話CS係咁多engine入面係計最少數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔同意<br />\n只係最少calculas<br />\nAlgorithm 有好多discreet math<br />\n甚至有好多大學既CS係under math department 架"},{"pid":"d80f5052d98c8e972634d26f10f5abf785541454","tid":26082,"uid":44501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T11:13:59.000Z","msg":"UST CS 比低gpa 人入<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />大部分course 都有GitHub source.照拎黎交就拎到100% assignment分，何來chur<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n學野既讀真正chur既H字尾course，咁可以year3讀elective，學下sql，scheme，基本hack人技巧，html 寫3個網，webGL一兩個月內屌隻game出黎，matlab試下call 圖象處理既function，入門既machine learning呢啲<br />\n咁year4就可以輕鬆返全職or 讀PG course咁<br />\nhea 既又唔怕grad唔到，反正乜7 cs既知識都靠inten學嫁啦<br />\n樓主你入到ust既其實可以考慮ust cs<br />\n唯一缺點係冇女"},{"pid":"94f78f2eab41b8d5b7739aa2b332ba931ec4801e","tid":26082,"uid":44501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T11:24:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>搭單問<br />\ncomputer science 同computer engineering有咩分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nphy同ict都有5 讀乜好科<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nce咪cs溝埋ee咁囉<br />\n但係ce係ee dept<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n都係果句 數底差唔好讀ee<br />\n係M2果d數唔係maths果d</blockquote><br />\n自問數底唔差唔勁<br />\n但係冇讀過m2<br />\n大電又唔夠分讀 嗚呀<br />\n咁mechanical engineering呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其他答你唔到<br />\n只可以話CS係咁多engine入面係計最少數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔同意<br />\n只係最少calculas<br />\nAlgorithm 有好多discreet math<br />\n甚至有好多大學既CS係under math department 架</blockquote><br />\n唔同意<br />\n計乜數都call api就搞掂<br />\nug algorithm都唔深入得去邊，考更多既係腦中模擬compiler <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\ncs係瘋狂接觸唔同language 同software， 然後搵工有得tick晒全部佢有問你識唔識既language，然後比班唔識cs既人教你做野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n讀b屎自學cs最好"},{"pid":"620fb89b100472ec5011662519ca2df21bfe713d","tid":26082,"uid":57006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T11:26:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>搭單問<br />\ncomputer science 同computer engineering有咩分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nphy同ict都有5 讀乜好科<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nce咪cs溝埋ee咁囉<br />\n但係ce係ee dept<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n都係果句 數底差唔好讀ee<br />\n係M2果d數唔係maths果d</blockquote><br />\n自問數底唔差唔勁<br />\n但係冇讀過m2<br />\n大電又唔夠分讀 嗚呀<br />\n咁mechanical engineering呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其他答你唔到<br />\n只可以話CS係咁多engine入面係計最少數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔同意<br />\n只係最少calculas<br />\nAlgorithm 有好多discreet math<br />\n甚至有好多大學既CS係under math department 架</blockquote><br />\n我覺得係algorithm 同 discreet math 同時用到同一類邏輯，例如set<br />\n唔係話algorithm 要計數嘅"},{"pid":"945af370e998ede6d4bdb279216b4a6f57eae7d4","tid":26082,"uid":23699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T12:39:21.000Z","msg":"覺得香港好多工讀IS 好過cs <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你要行好technical路線另計"},{"pid":"d8721557f36a9b38194624890d882a5820e5c79d","tid":26082,"uid":22116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T12:43:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>搭單問<br />\ncomputer science 同computer engineering有咩分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nphy同ict都有5 讀乜好科<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nce咪cs溝埋ee咁囉<br />\n但係ce係ee dept<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n都係果句 數底差唔好讀ee<br />\n係M2果d數唔係maths果d</blockquote><br />\n自問數底唔差唔勁<br />\n但係冇讀過m2<br />\n大電又唔夠分讀 嗚呀<br />\n咁mechanical engineering呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其他答你唔到<br />\n只可以話CS係咁多engine入面係計最少數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔同意<br />\n只係最少calculas<br />\nAlgorithm 有好多discreet math<br />\n甚至有好多大學既CS係under math department 架</blockquote><br />\n我覺得係algorithm 同 discreet math 同時用到同一類邏輯，例如set<br />\n唔係話algorithm 要計數嘅</blockquote><br />\n視乎CS想專邊範啦<br />\n單係common既discret math個D真係唔係好算數<br />\n但如果讀ML/BigData, image processing, alg. analysis, 之類個D用數讀到食屎<br />\n利申食過2舊屎"},{"pid":"da9d069387cf3a563c428fe60ebf1af3376a878a","tid":26082,"uid":15320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T12:51:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>搭單問<br />\n<br />\ncomputer science 同computer engineering有咩分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nphy同ict都有5 讀乜好科<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nce咪cs溝埋ee咁囉<br />\n但係ce係ee dept<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n都係果句 數底差唔好讀ee<br />\n係M2果d數唔係maths果d</blockquote><br />\n喺CU CE係跟CS Department<br />\n成個Department叫CSE"},{"pid":"e92b7332a5c41293464cc85c68a48f1015871451","tid":26082,"uid":15320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T12:52:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>入cu會唔會gpa太低揀唔到cs<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？</blockquote><br />\n入唔到CS入咗CE就喊三聲<br />\n個個Major Course都唔開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"701db66774fd8c6276ceb2aec6689b034a5bec5e","tid":26082,"uid":7744,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T12:53:04.000Z","msg":"City讀乜都垃圾架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"067310ca0e6582e6ddbaeacfc5cad78498d39abf","tid":26082,"uid":18384,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T12:59:15.000Z","msg":"傻既先諗，好人好姐點會讀city"}]}